  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Soak the umeboshi plums in water for at least 2 hours, then drain and pat dry.",
    "Mix the saffron rice with turmeric, cumin, and a pinch of salt in a bowl.",
    "Roast the umeboshi plums on a baking sheet with olive oil, salt, and crushed red pepper at 400°F (200°C) for 10 minutes.",
    "Steam the umeboshi plums in leaf wraps on top of the saffron rice mixture for 10 minutes.",
    "Grate the ginger and mix with the steamed umeboshi plums.",
    "Stir in the pistachio paste and mix until combined.",
    "Mix the coconut cream with a pinch of salt and a sprinkle of black pepper.",
    "To assemble, place a scoop of the saffron rice mixture on a plate, top with a few pieces of the roasted umeboshi plums, and garnish with chopped cilantro (if desired).",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
